Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
1. A newspaper asks two of its staff to review the coffee quality at \
different
trendy caf\[EAcute]s. The coffee can be rated on a scale from 1 (miserable) \
to 10 (excellent).
The results of the two coffee enthusiasts X and Y are as follows:\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9471186994262543`*^9, 
  3.947118733473477*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"580d60fb-7b96-4e14-bb0b-\
