Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
(a) Calculate and interpret Spearman\[CloseCurlyQuote]s rank correlation \
coefficient with pen and paper and then check your results using Mathematica.
(b) Does Spearman\[CloseCurlyQuote]s R differ depending on whether ranks are \
assigned in a decreasing
or increasing order?
(c) Suppose the coffee can only be rated as either good (>5) or bad (\
\[LessEqual]5). Do the
chances of a good rating differ between the two journalists?\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.947118770513743*^9, {3.947119030296616*^9, 
   3.947119043715526*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"1164e75f-e2d5-4e7d-ba58-\
39503372785f"],

Cell["Solution to (a) :", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.947119149836227*^9, 
  3.947119160988316*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"757d6db0-aa47-4c88-87ae-\
58820296d6c5"],

